# Task Priority System

Add priority levels to tasks so users can focus on what matters most.

## US-001: Add priority field to database
- [ ] Add priority column to tasks table: 'high' | 'medium' | 'low' (default 'medium')
- [ ] Generate and run migration successfully
- [ ] Typecheck passes

## US-002: Display priority badge on task cards
- [ ] Colored priority badge (red=high, yellow=medium, gray=low)
- [ ] Priority visible in list view without hovering
- [ ] Typecheck passes

## US-003: Add priority selector to task edit form
- [ ] Priority dropdown in task edit modal
- [ ] Saves on selection change
- [ ] Typecheck passes
